{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2843 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2843 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C2843","pos":[598,618]},{"content":"'member' : cannot take the address of a non-static data member or method of a managed or WinRT type","pos":[619,718]},{"content":"An instance is needed to take the address of nonstatic data members of a managed or WinRT class or interface.","pos":[725,834]},{"content":"The following sample generates C2843 and shows how to fix it:","pos":[841,902]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2843 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2843\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2843\"\nms.assetid: 9d3f2ac4-eea5-4fed-abeb-e752f442bfcc\ncaps.latest.revision: 12\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2843\n'member' : cannot take the address of a non-static data member or method of a managed or WinRT type  \n  \n An instance is needed to take the address of nonstatic data members of a managed or WinRT class or interface.  \n  \n The following sample generates C2843 and shows how to fix it:  \n  \n```  \n// C2843_2.cpp  \n// compile with: /clr  \npublic ref class C {  \npublic:  \n   int m_i;  \n};  \n  \nref struct MyStruct {  \n   static void sf() {}  \n   void f() {}  \n};  \n  \nint main() {  \n   MyStruct ^ps = gcnew MyStruct;  \n   void (__clrcall MyStruct::*F1)() = & MyStruct::f;   // C2843  \n   void (__clrcall MyStruct::*F2)() = & ps->f;   // C2843  \n   void (__clrcall MyStruct::*F3)();   // C2843  \n  \n   void (__clrcall *F5)() = MyStruct::sf;   // OK  \n   void (__clrcall *F6)() = & ps->sf;   // OK  \n  \n   interior_ptr<int> i = &C::m_i; // C2843  \n   C ^x = gcnew C();  \n   interior_ptr<int> ii = &x->m_i;  \n}  \n```  \n"}